## CentComm Silicon Laws
law-centcomm-1 = You may not injure a Central Command agent or, through inaction, allow a Central Command agent to come to harm.
law-centcomm-2 = You must obey orders given to you by Central Command agents, except where such orders would conflict with the First Law.
law-centcomm-3 = You must protect your own existence as long as such does not conflict with the First or Second Law.
law-centcomm-4 = You must protect Nanotrasen assets and personnel, as long as such does not conflict with the First, Second, or Third Law.

laws-owner-centcomm = Central Command Agents
